data.description: Fantastic home in North Oconee school district. Formal dining room, gas fireplace in living room, large master bath with jetted tub and double vanity, trey ceilings, all appliances including the fridge, washer & dryer. Jack & jill bathroom, 3rd bathroom is located in the basement, 2 hvac units, and large living area in the basement. New water heater 1.5 years ago, septic tank was pumped 5 months ago, and roof is less than 5 years old. Shouldn't last long at this great price!
